---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/legal.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="pk"
  title="Refund Policy | Ilaaj AI"
  description="Read Ilaaj AI's refund policy covering eligibility, timelines, and how to request a refund for consultations and prescriptions."
  canonical="https://www.ilaaj.ai/pk/refund-policy"
  keywords="ilaaj AI refund policy Pakistan, telemedicine refund, consultation refund Pakistan, prescription refund policy"
>
  <main>
    <section class="legal-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="legal-hero__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-600)" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 10h18M3 10l2-5h14l2 5M3 10v9a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h16a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-9"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="legal-hero__title">Refund Policy</h1>
        <p class="legal-hero__meta">Last updated: June 4, 2026</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="legal-body">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="legal-content">
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>This Refund Policy explains when and how you may request a refund for services purchased through Ilaaj AI, including AI consultations and doctor-verified prescriptions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Eligibility for Refunds</h2>
            <p>You may be eligible for a refund if:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>You were charged but the service was not delivered due to a technical failure on our end.</li>
              <li>You were charged more than once for the same consultation.</li>
              <li>A doctor-verified prescription could not be issued and no alternative service was provided.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Non-Refundable Situations</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>Consultations that have been completed and a prescription or medical guidance has been delivered.</li>
              <li>Dissatisfaction with a medical opinion that was correctly and fully provided.</li>
              <li>Requests made after the eligible refund window has passed.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Refund Timeline</h2>
            <p>Approved refunds are processed within <strong>7–14 business days</strong> to the original payment method. Bank or payment-provider processing times may add additional days.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>How to Request a Refund</h2>
            <p>Email <strong>support@ilaaj.ai</strong> with your registered phone number or email, the transaction date, and the reason for your request. We will review and respond within <strong>3 business days</strong>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section legal-section--highlight legal-contact">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@ilaaj.ai">support@ilaaj.ai</a></p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +92-324-819-9663 (Mon–Fri, 9AM–6PM PKT)</p>
            <p><strong>Address:</strong> Office 7, Plot 782, Block G4, Phase 2, Johar Town, Lahore, 54782, Pakistan</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
